title: Manndible Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located within Mann Library on the Cornell University campus, this cafe uses locally grown ingredients and fair trade coffee. Offers many vegetarian food and a burrito bar with tofu and seitan fillings. Vegan food include a tofu burrito and a tofu scramble. Toffuti soy cream cheese option for bagels, and vegan pastries and chocolates are often available. All muffins are vegan. Soy milk is substitutable for all drinks.
streetAddress: Albert R. Mann Library, Cornell University
